name: BACK BAY APARTMENT ON MARLBOROUGH ST
description:
BACK BAY studio apartment on prestigious Marlborough St close to hospitals.
Apartment has a queen mahogany murphy bed, breakfast bar, and stainless steel appliances.
Walk to all Boston has to offer. You can walk Newbury St, the subway, Boylston St, Copley Place, Boston Public Garden, downtown, North End, South End, Fenway Park and so much more.
